title: Baltimore police say they can't confirm or debunk Dr. Ben Carson's Popeye's robbery story
text: Baltimore police said Thursday they can't locate a police report in which Dr. Ben Carson was a victim in the robbery of a Popeye's -- but they're not saying the stick-up didn't happen. Police released a 24-page letter to the media documenting their efforts to find the report, which included searches... ...
